<subSubSection pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="16.[189,303,623,649]" box="[189,303,623,649]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<heading bold="true" box="[189,303,623,649]" fontSize="11" level="3" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" reason="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,303,623,649]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Remarks</emphasis>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="16.[189,1399,671,845]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
This species was originally described in 
<taxonomicName authority="(Costa 1864)" baseAuthorityName="Costa" baseAuthorityYear="1864" box="[649,963,671,698]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Sclerodermus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[649,809,671,697]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Sclerodermus</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Costa A. C. H." box="[821,955,671,698]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="1 - 176" refId="ref7289" refString="Costa A. C. H. 1864. Anno II - 1862 con quattro tavole. Parte prima et seconda. Annuario del Museo Zoologico della R. Universita di Napoli 2: 1 - 176." type="journal article" year="1864">Costa 1864</bibRefCitation>
)
</taxonomicName>
based on one female from 
<collectingCountry box="[1266,1322,671,697]" name="Italy" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Italy</collectingCountry>
. It was transferred to 
<taxonomicName box="[357,456,709,734]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[357,456,709,734]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Mesitius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation author="Kieffer J. - J." box="[504,678,708,734]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="228 - 595" refId="ref7541" refString="Kieffer J. - J. 1914. Bethylidae. Das Tierreich 41: 228 - 595." type="journal article" year="1914">Kieffer (1914)</bibRefCitation>
, who synonymised 
<taxonomicName box="[915,1214,708,734]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Sclerodermus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mutilloides">
<emphasis box="[915,1214,708,734]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Sclerodermus mutilloides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
under 
<taxonomicName authority="Spinola, 1851" authorityName="Spinola" authorityYear="1851" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="ghilianii">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Mesitius ghilianii</emphasis>
Spinola, 1851
</taxonomicName>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Argaman Q." box="[479,675,745,771]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="61 - 96" refId="ref7029" refString="Argaman Q. 2003. Generic synopsis of Mesitinae Kieffer, 1914 (Hymenoptera: Bethylidae). Entomofauna 24: 61 - 96." type="journal article" year="2003">Argaman (2003)</bibRefCitation>
revalidated the status as a valid species and transferred this species from 
<taxonomicName box="[348,447,783,808]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[348,447,783,808]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Mesitius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Nagy" authorityYear="1972" box="[488,627,782,808]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Clytrovorus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[488,627,782,808]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Clytrovorus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Argaman also established the synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authority="Kieffer, 1906" authorityName="Kieffer" authorityYear="1906" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fuscicornis">
<emphasis box="[1162,1399,782,808]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Mesitius fuscicornis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Kieffer J. - J." box="[189,341,819,845]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="289 - 551" refId="ref7501" refString="Kieffer J. - J. 1906. Proctotrypides. In: Andre E. (ed.) Species des hymenopteres d'Europe &amp; d'Algerie. Vol. 9: 289 - 551. A. Hermann, Paris." type="journal article" year="1906">Kieffer,1906</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Hoffer, 1936" authorityName="Hoffer" authorityYear="1936" box="[353,642,819,845]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="zavadili">
<emphasis box="[353,485,819,845]" italics="true" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">M. zavadili</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Hoffer A." box="[492,642,819,845]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" pagination="119 - 124" refId="ref7411" refString="Hoffer A. 1936. Rod Mesitius Thoms. v Ceskoslovenske republice. Genus Mesitius Thoms. in der Cechoslovakei. (Bethylidae, Hym. - Vespoid.). Acta Societatis entomologicae cechosloveniae 33: 119 - 124." type="journal article" year="1936">Hoffer, 1936</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authority="Nagy, 1968" authorityName="Nagy" authorityYear="1968" box="[699,951,819,845]" class="Insecta" family="Bethylidae" genus="Mesitius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viator">
